LogWhy                  Yes
SyslogFacility          mail

Syslog                  Yes
SyslogSuccess           Yes
TemporaryDirectory      /var/tmp
UMask                   022

SoftwareHeader          Yes
ReportAddress           someone@domain.tld
OversignHeaders         From
Quarantine              Yes
KeyTable                refile:/opt/hermes/dkim/KeyTable
